description:
I imagine Dualism into visual arts. Telling the difference is beautiful and fun. Being different and contradicting can be scary at times, but when I realize this is a growing life, it will be fun.

So are differences as varied as the amazing colors. Let me imagine if I lived only in white. this will be scary.

The woman behind the monster mask that symbolizes the mighty man is a symbol of difference that gives a sense of security and fun in this life.
